stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Loading: mount(resource)
    
    Loading --> Creating: resource not exists
    Loading --> Editing: resource exists
    
    Creating --> FormEntry: Initialize empty pendingFiles/pendingDeleteMedia
    Editing --> FormEntry: Load translations & existing media
    
    FormEntry --> LanguageSwitch: Change selectedLanguage
    LanguageSwitch --> FormEntry
    
    FormEntry --> FileUpload: Upload new files
    FileUpload --> PendingFilesQueue: updatedPendingFiles()
    PendingFilesQueue --> FormEntry: Add to pendingFiles[lang]
    
    FormEntry --> RemovePending: removePendingFile(lang, idx)
    RemovePending --> FormEntry: Remove from pendingFiles[lang]
    
    FormEntry --> MarkDelete: markDeleteMedia(mediaId, lang)
    MarkDelete --> PendingDeleteQueue: Add to pendingDeleteMedia[lang]
    PendingDeleteQueue --> FormEntry: Mark for deletion
    
    FormEntry --> Validating: save()
    
    Validating --> Saving: Validation Success
    Validating --> FormEntry: Validation Failed
    
    Saving --> MediaUpload: Save resource
    MediaUpload --> ProcessPendingFiles: Process each language
    ProcessPendingFiles --> AddMediaFiles: Upload files to translation
    AddMediaFiles --> ProcessDeletions: Files uploaded
    
    ProcessDeletions --> DeleteMarkedMedia: Process pendingDeleteMedia[lang]
    DeleteMarkedMedia --> ClearQueues: Delete media files
    ClearQueues --> SuccessToast: Clear pendingFiles & pendingDeleteMedia
    
    SuccessToast --> FormEntry: Update mode (stay on page)
    SuccessToast --> [*]: Create mode (redirect to edit)
    
    FormEntry --> [*]: Cancel (redirect to list)
    
    note right of FormEntry
        - Multi-language tabs (title)
        - Display existing files per language
        - Show pending upload files
        - Mark files for deletion
        - File upload input (PDF, DOC, DOCX, images)
    end note
    
    note right of PendingFilesQueue
        - Store files temporarily
        - Per-language array
        - Multiple file support
        - Display with remove option
    end note
    
    note right of PendingDeleteQueue
        - Mark existing media for deletion
        - Per-language array
        - Visual indication (strikethrough)
        - Delayed deletion on save
    end note
    
    note right of MediaUpload
        - Get translation by locale
        - Add media with original filename
        - Store in 'resources' collection
        - Process all languages
    end note
    
    note right of DeleteMarkedMedia
        - Find media by ID
        - Delete from translation
        - Process all marked files
        - Clear queue after deletion
    end note
